Where this Transformation Takes Place: Valtharixs Demonic Leviathan form can only fully manifest in places where the boundaries between realms are blurred, such as the Abyssal Aquasphere or the Oceanic Expanse. These locations possess the primal elemental energy required for the transformation, enhancing Valtharixâ€™s powers. In these domains, the sea bends to his will, and the Abyssal energies elevate his infernal nature, making him nearly unstoppable.
