Player Backstories 

Demons 

Valtharix (Mitchell) 

Valtharix: From Outcast to Arcane Innovator 

Origins & Early Curiosity 

Valtharix was born from a primordial surge of arcane energyâ€”a being of raw, untamed magic whose early existence was marked by an innate wonder. In his youth, driven by an insatiable curiosity, he stumbled upon ancient, forbidden texts hidden deep in lost libraries and secret vaults. These dark tomesâ€”filled with esoteric incantations and secrets deemed too dangerous for ordinary magesâ€”ignited a passion for knowledge that set him apart. This early exposure to forbidden lore not only broadened his magical horizons but also isolated him from his peers, as he began questioning conventional teachings and seeking truths that most would never dare approach. 

Mentorship and the Seeds of Betrayal 

During this formative period, Valtharix encountered a mysterious mentorâ€”a venerable sorcerer reputed for his mastery over the deepest mysteries of magic. Under the mentorâ€™s tutelage, Valtharix learned advanced techniques and gained insights into arcane disciplines that few could comprehend. However, as his power grew, so did the mentorâ€™s ambitions. A catastrophic experimentâ€”an ill-fated attempt to harness cosmic energiesâ€”led to the mentorâ€™s tragic downfall. This betrayal left an indelible mark on Valtharix, teaching him to be cautious about trust and fueling his determination to surpass even those he once revered. 

The Weight of Ancestry and Cultural Legacy 

Even as he forged his own path, Valtharix could not escape the influence of his ancestral legacy. Whispers of his forebearsâ€”legendary figures whose feats were woven into the fabric of magical historyâ€”haunted his every step. Their triumphs and, equally, their failures became a benchmark against which he measured his own ambitions. This cultural inheritance compelled him to blend ancient traditions with revolutionary ideas, ensuring that his innovations would not only break new ground but also honor the wisdom of the past. 

Internal Struggles and Moral Ambiguity 

As Valtharixâ€™s research and power grew, he found himself caught in a relentless internal conflict. Each breakthrough in his quest for forbidden knowledge came at a costâ€”forcing him to confront the ethical implications of his experiments. There were moments of deep self-doubt, where the line between ambition and recklessness blurred. The same arcane energies that promised salvation could, if uncontrolled, lead to chaos. This constant moral tug-of-war imbued his journey with complexity and nuance, driving him to master his craft not only to protect the outcasts but also to ensure that his power would be wielded responsibly. 

Exile and the Birth of the Eternum Bastion 

Venturing forth with a message of peace and unity, Valtharix soon encountered widespread fear. Ancient governments and rival factions across dimensionsâ€”the Exalted Concord, the Umbral Pact, the Ashen Covenant, the Seekers of the Lost Name, and the dominant ruling bodiesâ€”mistook his overwhelming power for a harbinger of chaos. Rejected and cast out, he withdrew into the void, determined to forge a new destiny far from the prejudiced glare of conventional realms. 

In isolation, he set about creating the Eternum Bastionâ€”a sanctuary where the outcasts and misunderstood could find refuge. Through a heavily modified version of the Rite of Eternal Binding, Valtharix sacrificed his mortal form and merged his soul with the very fabric of the Bastion. This monumental ritual not only secured his immortality but transformed the fortress into a living entityâ€”its every corridor, chamber, and ward now imbued with his indomitable will. 

A Beacon of Innovation and Unity 

Over time, the Eternum Bastion evolved beyond a mere safe haven into the pinnacle of arcane innovation. Its vast halls now house specialized research roomsâ€”from the Chronomancerâ€™s Observatory and the Elemental Convergence Chamber to the Necrotic Synthesis Wing, the Enigmatic Illusions Hall, the Artifact Forging Foundry, the Planar Gateway Nexus, the Celestial Observation Chamber, and the Verdant Sanctum. Each room contributes a unique â€œNodeâ€ (a scaled-down version of its signature device) that channels its specialty into a vast magical network. When activated together, these Nodes form a complex Hexcasting pattern that amplifies research, fortifies defenses, and monitors arcane phenomenaâ€”demonstrating the Bastionâ€™s harmonious blend of innovation and tradition. 

Opposition and the Council of Arcane Oversight 

Despite the Bastionâ€™s glowing promise of progress, ancient factions and ruling powers continue to oppose Valtharixâ€™s methods. Groups such as the Exalted Concord, Umbral Pact, Ashen Covenant, and Seekers of the Lost Name decry his unorthodox methods, while the Galpolkan Tribunal and Elysian Vanguard demand strict oversight of his innovations. To manage these conflicts, Valtharix established the Council of Arcane Oversightâ€”a body that unites leading researchers from the Arcane Academy, representatives from the Elysian Vanguard and Galpolkan Tribunal, and his personal advisors. This council ensures responsible innovation and acts as a political bridge between traditional power and revolutionary change. 

Alliances for a New Era 

Valtharixâ€™s vision, though contested by many, has attracted powerful allies who share his dream of a unified future: 

The Stellar Navigators harness interdimensional travel to explore and map uncharted realms, expanding the Bastionâ€™s influence. 

The Keepers of the Verdant Grove nurture the natural energies of the Verdant Sanctum, ensuring that the Bastionâ€™s innovations remain grounded in the rhythms of life. 

The Radiant Covenant preserves ancient wisdom and helps integrate traditional practices with modern advancements, bridging the old and the new. 

The Future: Thaumaturgic Mechanomancy 

Together, these allies form the backbone of what may one day be known as Thaumaturgic Mechanomancyâ€”a harmonious fusion of traditional arcane wisdom, cutting-edge magitek, and innovative Hexcasting. Although this paradigm shift remains a potential future development, its early influences are already visible in the Bastionâ€™s evolving architecture and research ethos. Valtharixâ€™s legacy is now one of both sanctuary and relentless innovationâ€”a destiny that promises to reshape the multiverse and elevate all those who have been cast aside. 

