Performed in the Abyssal Foundry, at the heart of the Bastionâ€™s forge. 

Purpose: To fuse oneâ€™s soul with a structure, making it an extension of their will. 

Offering: Oneâ€™s entire mortal formâ€”body, mind, and spirit. 

 

The Ritualâ€™s Execution 

The Construction of the Core 

Before the ritual began, Valtharix spent centuries refining the materials that would house his essence. Using forbidden alloys, void-forged metals, and enchanted obsidian, he created a Heartstone, an artifact designed to serve as the Bastionâ€™s central core, housing his very soul. 

