The Tempest Warden â€“ A titanic, semi-transparent figure of storm and lightning, its form ever-shifting between a humanoid guardian and a living thundercloud. It tests those who seek the power of the Aerie, unleashing gale-force winds and strikes of golden lightning upon intruders. 

